{"tid":535747,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fb打擊假新聞　修改動態消息排序","createTime":"2018-01-21T07:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T05:38:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fe177a02a9980b0177d55b0a577062c185eacaff","tid":535747,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180121/20280967?_ga=2.190252715.1484461583.1516254068-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F20280967%3F_ga%3D2.190252715.1484461583.1516254068-581282530.1504247435&d=QaAlz3VG9psVBQmHWv3ogf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=4f36a789\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F20280967%3F_ga%3D2.190252715.1484461583.1516254068-581282530.1504247435&h=8a008fe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180121/20280967?_ga=2.190252715.1484461583.1516254068-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfb打擊假新聞　修改動態消息排序<br />\n<br />\n2,012<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180121/large/chris92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180121%2Flarge%2Fchris92.jpg&h=a54f8ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n號稱有20億活躍用戶的社交網站facebook，再有打擊假新聞措施，修改「動態消息」（News Feed）排序方式，優先顯示來源可信的新聞消息，至於來源的可信度，則透過對用戶進行調查來決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前日fb在網誌公佈，早前已就新聞來源可信度問題，抽樣調查了「多元化、具代表性」美國用戶，會在本周開始改變排序方式，先在美國進行，之後會推展到全球。<br />\n<br />\nfb「教主」朱克伯格（圖）發帖稱：「當前全球太多譁眾取寵、假資訊和兩極化情況。社交媒體讓人前所未有地迅速散播消息。若不針對解決這些問題，會令這些現象變本加厲。」惟評定新聞來源可信度的用戶是否公正、或是否能夠辨識新聞質素優劣，都左右評審結果。代表美加2,000傳媒機構的「新聞媒體聯盟」就指fb措施雖然正面，但效果成疑。<br />\n<br />\n本月較早前fb已宣佈對「動態消息」作出大改革，將親友帖文提前顯示，優先於傳媒、商業機構和名人用戶發佈的非廣告資訊。<br />\n<br />\n假新聞氾濫，不只fb用戶受害，Twitter亦表示發現其美國用戶當中，有多達67.7萬人在前年美國大選投票日之前，曾經轉推、讚好或追隨源自俄羅斯的宣傳推文。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n英少年冒認CIA局長竊美軍事機密<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n印度五日五宗強姦　受害女童最小僅三歲"},{"pid":"f311162ca102f859d95c264ff0dc4041cea9b23c","tid":535747,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caf42a1bfb87baac81b864524f669c1482811b7","tid":535747,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"印度五日五宗強姦　受害女童最小僅三歲"},{"pid":"1a8f9295123702beee228b9e8c2104042eda91fb","tid":535747,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"打壓就打壓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔俾錢嘅就撳低reach數"},{"pid":"c2330427e291574b8287c584e2cccb4395097d0b","tid":535747,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"有人話係想鋪路入大陸"},{"pid":"e174cb4eecafff0c332da52b74787f59cf86370d","tid":535747,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"唔係官方文章咪就係fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067fee147e7edc2c99ec52bb2fb9c37c4fb0b741","tid":535747,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"英少年冒認CIA局長竊美軍事機密<br />\n想睇依個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6fbfcfc15ce0a794898ccd77fdf168f79242a0","tid":535747,"uid":41969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"無俾保護費俾fb= fake news"},{"pid":"733a9426812f9a450813f4b85f01fdcab8c0548f","tid":535747,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:38:14.000Z","msg":"新聞係咪假係向用戶調查 ? 咩邏輯 ?<br />\n同埋社交網絡係拎黎貼新聞既平台 ?"}]}